import React from "react";
import "./Todos.css"
import data from "../../mock-data.json";

const Todos = () => {
	return (
		<>
			<form>

				<input
					type="text"
					placeholder="Enter your fullname"
					name="fullname"
					required
				/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					placeholder="Enter an adress"
					name="adress"
					required
				/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					placeholder="Enter a phonenumber"
					name="phoneNumber"
					required
				/>
				<input 
					type=""
				/>
			</form>
		</>
	);
};

export default Todos;
